column5: Fishing this weekend was pretty consistent.  We never smashed them at any point but it was steady catching, and as always there were better times than others.  For the weekend, we managed close to 20 whities and only 3 small lakers haha. No herring this weekend at all, I dont think we even marked one.  Kind of a nice change. Fish caught on the usual, williams spoons, tubes and laker takers.  Fished 88-95 feet Got a few of the fish on video for you guys to have a peak at.  http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aR7mGh4i29Q
Nice video steve!!!!!!!  im saving all my big fish for after feb 1st.lol
watching that video got me pumped for my trip that is coming up this week on nippissing!
Nice work Steve, may have to blast over to your side of the lake and drill right beside your hut LOL. R
Ya because that hasnt happened 10 times this week
Nice!!!  Always Good to get 'Customers' into Fish
Way to go Steve! Nice seeing the whities making an appearance for you.
